To build the project install the dependencies in requirements.txt

If you want to isolate the environment to deploy, use virtualenv and virtualenvwrapper.

pip install -U virtualenvwrapper
export WORKON_HOME=~/.virtualenvs
mkdir -p $WORKON_HOME
source /usr/local/bin/virtualenvwrapper.sh
mkvirtualenv funfinabox
pip install -r requirements.txt


Required environment variables:
DROPBOX_APP_KEY
DROPBOX_APP_SECRET